@startuml
!include _yunlink_protocol_theme.iuml
title sunray_yunlink_bridge - Component View

package "sunray_yunlink_bridge" <<Neutral>> {
  component "bridge_node" as Node <<Control>>
  component "ros_adapter" as RosAdapter <<StatePlane>>
  component "yunlink_adapter" as YunAdapter <<Control>>
  component "command_tracker" as Tracker <<Control>>
}

package "Sunray ROS Contract" <<Neutral>> {
  component "px4_state" as Px4 <<StatePlane>>
  component "odom_status" as Odom <<StatePlane>>
  component "fsm/state" as Fsm <<StatePlane>>
  component "controller_state" as Ctrl <<StatePlane>>
  component "uav_control_cmd" as Cmd <<Control>>
}

package "yunlink::Runtime" <<Control>> {
  component "external command mode" as RuntimeMode <<Control>>
  component "typed inbound command\nsubscriber" as RuntimeSub <<Control>>
  component "explicit command\nresult reply helper" as RuntimeReply <<Control>>
}

Node --> RosAdapter : pull latest states /\npublish raw command
Node --> YunAdapter : validate / publish /\nreply result
Node --> Tracker : infer InProgress /\nSucceeded / Failed

RosAdapter --> Px4
RosAdapter --> Odom
RosAdapter --> Fsm
RosAdapter --> Ctrl
RosAdapter --> Cmd

YunAdapter --> RuntimeMode
YunAdapter --> RuntimeSub
YunAdapter --> RuntimeReply

note right of Tracker
只跟踪一期 raw control 命令：
Takeoff / Land / Return /
Goto / VelocitySetpoint
end note
@enduml
